638,MICs Group of Health Services,"Equity, Diversity, Inclusivity & Belonging","Equity, Diversity, Inclusivity & Belonging. NF. • Continue to build upon equity, diversity, inclusivity & belonging culture.",HEALTH EQUITY & SOCIAL ACCOUNTABILITY,ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,"The text directly mentions equity, diversity, and inclusion, and building a related culture implicates organizational values and governance.",Health Equity & Social Accountability,Health Equity & Social Accountability,Small Hospital,FALSE,3,MICs Group of Health Services,638
