638,MICs Group of Health Services,Safety,Safety. NF. • Promote a just culture.: • Build capacity and knowledge to mitigate workplace violence.: • Leverage technology to enhance patient/resident safety.,PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,WORKFORCE SUSTAINABILITY,"The text emphasizes patient and resident safety, while also addressing workplace violence, which impacts workforce well-being and capacity.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Small Hospital,FALSE,3,MICs Group of Health Services,638
