790,Hotel Dieu Shaver HEALTH AND REHABILITATION CENTRE,Enhance Research And Innovation,Enhance Research And Innovation. We will expand academic and industry leader partnerships to advance research and innovation in rehabilitation.. NF.,"RESEARCH, EDUCATION & ACADEMICS",INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,The focus is on expanding research and innovation through partnerships with academic and industry leaders.,"Research, Education & Academics","Research, Education & Academics",Chronic/Rehab Hospital,FALSE,1,Hotel Dieu Shaver HEALTH AND REHABILITATION CENTRE,790
790,Hotel Dieu Shaver HEALTH AND REHABILITATION CENTRE,Sustain Exceptional Quality And Patient Experience,"Sustain Exceptional Quality And Patient Experience. We will ensure long-term sustainability of high-quality care and exceptional patient experience inspired by comfort, care, and hope.. NF.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,FINANCIAL SUSTAINABILITY,"The text emphasizes maintaining high-quality patient care and experience while also mentioning long-term sustainability, which implies financial considerations.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Chronic/Rehab Hospital,FALSE,1,Hotel Dieu Shaver HEALTH AND REHABILITATION CENTRE,790
793,St. Thomas Elgin General Hospital,Partnering With Patients,"Partnering With Patients. We will engage patient and caregivers in a meaningful way to enhance their experiences, facilitate self-care, and improve quality and safety of care.. Involve patients and families in co-design initiatives across the organization to enhance the patient experience: Advance a culture of belonging for everyone where we foster Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion to reflect the people we serve: Enhance safety and quality of care while engaging patients and families across their care journey: Develop a comprehensive engagement framework that facilitates meaningful participation and collaboration with patients: Integrate Diversity, Equity, Inclusion (DEI) into every aspect of organizational practice based on patient experience feedback: Enhance Indigenous Engagement and Inclusion Strategy: Create guidelines and protocols to adopt and sustain evidence-based best practices while prioritizing patient safety and quality of care.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,HEALTH EQUITY & SOCIAL ACCOUNTABILITY,"The focus is on improving patient experience, quality, and safety of care, with a strong emphasis on diversity, equity, inclusion, and Indigenous engagement.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,St. Thomas Elgin General Hospital,793
793,St. Thomas Elgin General Hospital,Creating Collaborative Networks,"Creating Collaborative Networks. We will collaborate with other service providers to co-design, support and deliver accessible and coordinated services for our patients, organization, and region. Advance our Cyber Security posture: Enhance Mental Health & Addictions Strategies: Optimize and build capacity toward an integrated health system by providing care closer to home: Develop and implement standardized policies, tools, and equipment for cyber security: Collaborate with community agencies and stakeholders to develop integrated Mental Health & Addiction services and reduce duplication across the region: Collaborate and strengthen relationships with regional partners and organizations.",INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,ACCESS & CAPACITY,"Focuses on collaboration with service providers to co-design and deliver accessible and coordinated services, with a secondary emphasis on optimizing capacity towards an integrated health system.",Integration & Partnerships,Integration & Partnerships,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,St. Thomas Elgin General Hospital,793
793,St. Thomas Elgin General Hospital,Empowering Our Team,"Empowering Our Team. We will ensure a safe and healthy workplace and invest in our team’s development to meet the evolving needs of our patients and our community. Create a safe, inspiring, inclusive and healthy workplace: Strengthen the stability of our workforce: Attract, retain and recognize our people as valuable members of our team: Build the capacity & capabilities of our teams to meet the needs of our patients with confidence: Enhance well-being and psychological safety of our staff: Ensure our teams reflect and are equipped to support the growing diversity of the community we serve: Develop focused strategies to retain and develop our current workforce and the workforce of the future: Focus on an engaged workforce where team members have the opportunity and skills to improve how their work is done.",WORKFORCE SUSTAINABILITY,ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,"The text focuses on creating a positive and supportive work environment, attracting and retaining staff, and enhancing their well-being, which aligns with workforce sustainability and organizational culture.",Workforce Sustainability,Workforce Sustainability,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,St. Thomas Elgin General Hospital,793
793,St. Thomas Elgin General Hospital,Achieving Operational Excellence,Achieving Operational Excellence. We will deliver quality care by adopting evidence-based practices while supporting the sustainability of our healthcare system. Strengthen internal information systems to improve service delivery and quality care: Optimize programs and services to better serve patients: Drive innovation to support operational sustainability to enable care and long-term growth: Enhance our clinical and corporate tools and systems: Improve access to care for all patients: Reduce the environmental impact of our hospital: Improve accountability for healthcare service delivery results: Collaborate with our community to continuously enhance the hospital: Continue to grow and foster a culture of Continuous Quality Improvement.,PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,FINANCIAL SUSTAINABILITY,"The text emphasizes quality care, evidence-based practices, sustainability of the healthcare system, and optimizing programs, indicating a focus on both patient care excellence and financial sustainability.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,St. Thomas Elgin General Hospital,793
824,Rural Roads Health Services,Our Strategic Priorities,"Our Strategic Priorities. NF. * Together, pursue fulsome organizational integration toward better patient care and best use of our resources: * Proud of our rural roots, as small and unique hospitals, advance our service delivery model: * With our partners, serve our communities exceptionally well by creating an integrated system: * We are powered by our people, and commit to supporting them to be at their best.",INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,The text emphasizes organizational integration and partnerships to improve patient care and resource utilization.,Integration & Partnerships,Integration & Partnerships,Small Hospital,FALSE,1,Rural Roads Health Services,824
