827,Baycrest,Redefine The Residential Living Experience For Older Persons,"Redefine The Residential Living Experience For Older Persons. Provide sector leadership through the introduction of transformative social, recreational and wellness programs and best-in-class health care services in all the hospital congregate residential settings locally, nationally and globally.. NF.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,POPULATION & COMMUNITY HEALTH,The text focuses on improving health care services and introducing wellness programs for older persons in residential settings.,Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Chronic/Rehab Hospital,FALSE,1,Baycrest,827
827,Baycrest,Be A Leading Voice In Advancing The Lives Of Older Persons,"Be A Leading Voice In Advancing The Lives Of Older Persons. Raise societal awareness and influence public policies that enhance the well-being of the world’s aging population, enabling older persons to explore their possibilities and live with purpose, fulfilment and dignity.. NF.",POPULATION & COMMUNITY HEALTH,HEALTH EQUITY & SOCIAL ACCOUNTABILITY,"Focuses on enhancing well-being and societal awareness for older persons, which relates to population health and addressing their needs with dignity and purpose, aligning with social accountability.",Population & Community Health,Population & Community Health,Chronic/Rehab Hospital,FALSE,1,Baycrest,827
