827,Baycrest,Innovation,Innovation. Innovation is in the hospital's DNA. We are driven by relentless curiosity on how to provide better care and better opportunities for the global aging population.. NF.,ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,"RESEARCH, EDUCATION & ACADEMICS","The text highlights innovation as a core value (""in the hospital's DNA"") and also references the hospital's commitment to improving care for a global population, suggesting a research focus.",Org Culture & Governance,Org Culture & Governance,Chronic/Rehab Hospital,FALSE,1,Baycrest,827
802,HÔPITAL Glengarry Memorial HOSPITAL,Quality & Safety,"Quality & Safety. Enrich the patient experience through quality, safe care that welcomes patients and families as partners in care.. • Advance Person & Family Centred Care, ensuring the patient voice is embedded throughout hospital programs and services.: • Provide culturally safe care for those who access our services and support health equity for racialized and marginalized people.: • Support safe care by assessing and addressing risk throughout the organization.: • Progress the implementation of the Best Practice Spotlight Organization commitments with an interprofessional approach.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,HEALTH EQUITY & SOCIAL ACCOUNTABILITY,"The text focuses on improving patient experience through quality and safe care, including culturally safe care and addressing health equity.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Small Hospital,FALSE,1,HÔPITAL Glengarry Memorial HOSPITAL,802
802,HÔPITAL Glengarry Memorial HOSPITAL,People & Culture,"People & Culture. Improve engagement by investing in the organizations people and empower a caring and positive culture for all.. Recruitment & Retention: Diversity, Equity, Inclusion & Reconciliation: Safety & Wellness: Professional & Leadership Development: Rewards and Recognition.",WORKFORCE SUSTAINABILITY,ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,"The text focuses on improving employee engagement, recruitment, retention, wellness, and fostering a positive culture, which aligns with workforce sustainability and organizational culture themes.",Workforce Sustainability,Workforce Sustainability,Small Hospital,FALSE,1,HÔPITAL Glengarry Memorial HOSPITAL,802
802,HÔPITAL Glengarry Memorial HOSPITAL,Integration & Standardization,"Integration & Standardization. Deliver standardized quality care in a cost-effective way through collaboration & integration opportunities.. • Engage in opportunities within the Great River Ontario Health Team that focus on system integration & collaboration which enhance the patient, family, and provider experience.: • Support patients and families through transitions in care with modernization, communication, and collaboration.: • Develop and sustain programs and services that meet the needs of the communities we serve by exploring optimal resource utilization and virtual care opportunities.",INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,"The focus is on integration & standardization through the OHT and collaboration, alongside delivering standardized quality care and enhancing patient experience.",Integration & Partnerships,Integration & Partnerships,Small Hospital,FALSE,1,HÔPITAL Glengarry Memorial HOSPITAL,802
802,HÔPITAL Glengarry Memorial HOSPITAL,Future Planning,"Future Planning. Invest in the sustainability of our equipment & infrastructure to support safe, quality care.. • Drive financial stabilization to address gaps in funding and identify new funding opportunities which support innovative care delivery models.: • Leverage and enhance equipment & technology for our patients to receive care close to home with support and collaboration from our partners.: • Engage in infrastructure renewal & capital redevelopment planning processes.",INFRASTRUCTURE & ENVIRONMENT,FINANCIAL SUSTAINABILITY,"The text focuses on equipment and infrastructure sustainability and renewal, along with financial stabilization to support care delivery.",Infrastructure & Environment,Infrastructure & Environment,Small Hospital,FALSE,1,HÔPITAL Glengarry Memorial HOSPITAL,802
804,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,Exceptional Patient Care,"Exceptional Patient Care. Every patient we serve will receive personalized, compassionate, and high-quality care. Supporting their healing, well-being and satisfaction throughout their healthcare journey.. We will provide high-quality, timely, safe and accessible care.: We will empower, involve and support patients and families in their care.: We will provide inclusive care that reflects the communities we serve.: Achieve zero preventable harm to patients: Work closely with partners to reduce barriers to care: Actively advance integrated care models.","PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE (Quality, safety, experience)","INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS (OHTs, system integration)","The primary focus is on delivering exceptional, high-quality, and safe patient care, with a secondary consideration for integrated care models through partnerships.","Patient Care Excellence (Quality, Safety, Experience)",Patient Care Excellence,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,804
804,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,Outstanding Team,"Outstanding Team. We strive to cultivate a skilled, engaged, and empowered workforce, fostering a culture of collaboration, professional development, and excellence to deliver the best possible outcomes for our patients and community.. We will be a great place to work and an employer of choice.: We will employ innovative recruitment and retention efforts to attract top talent.: We will support team health and well-being.: We will invest in the development of our team and foster a culture of continuous learning.: Recruiting partnerships that sustainably meet hiring needs: Excellent staff well-being and workplace culture: Expanded staff development, education and up-skilling opportunities: A workforce that is representative of our community and embraces inclusion, diversity and equity.",WORKFORCE SUSTAINABILITY,ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,"The text focuses on creating a positive work environment, attracting and retaining talent, and supporting staff well-being and development, while also touching on the importance of a representative and inclusive workforce.",Workforce Sustainability,Workforce Sustainability,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,804
804,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,Operational Excellence,"Operational Excellence. Our aim is to optimize efficiency, effectiveness, and safety in all aspects of our operations. Leveraging best practices, technology, and continuous improvement initiatives to achieve the highest standards of service delivery and resource management.. We will grow and improve our infrastructure and services to reflect the needs of the communities we serve and elevate patient care.: We will ensure the responsible financial management and stewardship of our resources.: We will ensure our facilities are safe for all those entering our doors.: We will continuously improve, informed by measurement, benchmarking and monitoring.: We will strengthen the link between THE_HOSPITAL and THE_HOSPITAL through integrated governance.: Exemplary patient, staff and medical staff satisfaction: Ever-improving heathcare outcomes: Financial stewardship.",FINANCIAL SUSTAINABILITY,PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,"The text focuses on optimizing efficiency, resource management, safety, and financial stewardship, as well as improving patient outcomes and satisfaction.",Financial Sustainability,Financial Sustainability,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,804
804,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,Community Partnerships And Connection,"Community Partnerships And Connection. We are committed to building strong partnerships and meaningful connections with our community stakeholders, collaborating to address local health needs, promote wellness, and enhance access to care through outreach, education, and advocacy.. We will engage with our communities and health and social care partners to improve care and advance the implementation of Ontario Health Teams.: We will support our foundation in fundraising to improve our infrastructure and services to meet the needs of our community.: We will increase community engagement and communication to ensure an understanding of our services and new developments at the hospital.: We will prioritize public health and bolster partnerships to address community health concerns and enhance overall well-being.: Seamless patient navigation and integration between hospital and community care: Expanded infrastructure and services: Enhanced community engagement.",INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,POPULATION & COMMUNITY HEALTH,"The text emphasizes building partnerships with community stakeholders, addressing local health needs, promoting wellness, and integrating hospital and community care, along with Ontario Health Teams.",Integration & Partnerships,Integration & Partnerships,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,804
804,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,Innovation And Digital Enablement,"Innovation And Digital Enablement. Embracing innovation and leveraging digital technologies, we seek to drive transformative change in healthcare delivery, enhancing accessibility, efficiency, and quality of care through the adoption of cutting-edge solutions and data-driven approaches.. We will implement a new electronic medical record system to streamline healthcare processes and enhance patient care and records management.: We will leverage innovation, digital technologies and data analytics to improve care quality, efficiency and patient-centredness.: We will advance and strengthen a culture of innovation and continuous improvement.: High-quality data and decision-making to deliver more efficient care: Improved patient, staff and medical staff experience: Increased accessibility and timeliness of care.",DIGITAL HEALTH & INNOVATION,PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,"The text emphasizes the use of digital technologies to improve healthcare delivery, accessibility, efficiency, and quality of care, with a focus on implementing a new EMR system and leveraging data analytics.",Digital Health & Innovation,Digital Health & Innovation,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Norfolk GENERAL HOSPITAL,804
