935,Thunder Bay Regional Health Sciences Centre<br>Thunder Bay Regional Health Research Institute,"Research, Innovation, & Learning","Research, Innovation, & Learning. Driven by the needs of our patients, our staff, and our communities. • Prioritize research and assess current research initiatives.: • Enable opportunities for knowledge translation.: • Recruit researchers to address staffing gaps.: • Retain current staff and mentor new researchers.: • Establish an evaluation framework.: • Encourage staff to lead and participate in research, innovation, and learning.: • Support continuous education and professional development.","RESEARCH, EDUCATION & ACADEMICS",WORKFORCE SUSTAINABILITY,"The text focuses on prioritizing research, knowledge translation, and supporting staff through education and mentorship in research, aligning with workforce sustainability by addressing staffing gaps and retention.","Research, Education & Academics","Research, Education & Academics",Teaching Hospital,FALSE,1,Thunder Bay Regional Health Sciences Centre<br>Thunder Bay Regional Health Research Institute,935
