948,The Centre for Addiction and Mental Health (CAMH),Advance Care,"Advance Care. Transform how patients and families experience care. Create new models of care. Improve health outcomes by learning from all that we do and by applying the evidence from our work with patients, partners and communities. Adopt and adapt the evidence created by others. Share our discoveries and learnings with the world.. • Leverage our strength as a comprehensive academic mental health centre to treat the most serious mental illness with programs that care for and support patients at all stages of life.: • Expand access to high-quality treatment and supports through seamless care pathways within our own programs and within the broader health care system.: • Drive precision health care—targeted to the individual needs of patients and families—using advancements in research, artificial intelligence and technology.: • Integrate teaching and research into clinical care, translating new discoveries into improved treatments faster.: • Complete THE_HOSPITAL’s historic redevelopment: construct the Secure Care and Recovery Building for patients in contact with the justice system and the Discovery Centre for world-leading research and innovation.: • Train the mental health teams of the future to ensure that they have the skills to meet the evolving needs of patients and families.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,"The text focuses on transforming patient experience and improving health outcomes, as well as expanding access through seamless pathways within and outside the hospital.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Chronic/Rehab Hospital,FALSE,1,The Centre for Addiction and Mental Health (CAMH),948
948,The Centre for Addiction and Mental Health (CAMH),Get Upstream,"Get Upstream. Build pathways for early interventions during critical moments across the lifespan to change the trajectory of illness and improve quality of life.. • Identify mental illness sooner and ensure timely access to care by forging connections across health, education and social sectors that build capacity for early intervention and prevention beyond the hospital setting.: • Invest in the healthy development of children, youth and emerging and young adults by facilitating rapid access to high-quality services, creating new treatments and working with partners to develop public health approaches to preventing mental illness.: • Advance knowledge of brain development and create innovative ways to intervene at key points in patients’ lives to promote brain health, improve outcomes and prevent people at all stages of life from developing serious and chronic illness.: • Adopt a public mental health approach that focuses on health promotion, prevention of mental illness and early intervention.",POPULATION & COMMUNITY HEALTH,INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,The text focuses on early interventions and prevention of mental illness across the lifespan by building connections across sectors.,Population & Community Health,Population & Community Health,Chronic/Rehab Hospital,FALSE,1,The Centre for Addiction and Mental Health (CAMH),948
948,The Centre for Addiction and Mental Health (CAMH),Lift Societal Health,"Lift Societal Health. Do our part to create a healthy and just Canadian society by addressing health disparities and ensuring mental and physical health outcomes are equitable for people living with mental illness.. • Be transparent and resolute in addressing health disparities that people from structurally marginalized groups face.: • Address the prejudice, discrimination and disparities that people who live with serious mental illness experience.: • Ensure at THE_HOSPITAL that we are equitable, diverse, inclusive, accessible and anti-racist.: • Expand services focused on First Nations, Inuit and Métis health through Shkaabe Makwa, and deepen our organizational commitment to Truth and Reconciliation.: • Prioritize the health of Black patients and families through partnerships with the Black community, expanded access to culturally responsive care and increased research.: • Invest in research, education, clinical care and action to respond to the compelling evidence that climate change impacts the developing brain and the mental health of people around the world.: • Amplify the voices of the mental health movement to create public policy that reduces health disparities and improves social determinants of health for everyone.",HEALTH EQUITY & SOCIAL ACCOUNTABILITY,POPULATION & COMMUNITY HEALTH,"The text focuses on addressing health disparities, promoting equity for marginalized groups, and improving social determinants of health for people with mental illness, as well as broader societal well-being.",Health Equity & Social Accountability,Health Equity & Social Accountability,Chronic/Rehab Hospital,FALSE,1,The Centre for Addiction and Mental Health (CAMH),948
947,University Health Network (UHN),Transformative Experiences,"Transformative Experiences. We will create extraordinary, integrated health care experiences that are seamless, compassionate and centered around the patient, family and THE_HOSPITAL members. Every individual – whether receiving care or delivering it – deserves an environment that supports their needs. Our aspiration is to create a system that puts people first, empowers our staff, and delivers on our promises at every touchpoint.. Integrated Care: Break down barriers and create a unified, seamless health care experience that travels with the patient, wherever they go.. THE_HOSPITAL Experience: Build an environment where our team members are empowered, valued and ready to take bold action, day in and day out.. Lead in Education: Create world-class educational experiences that prepare the next generation of clinicians and scientists to push the limits of possibility.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,"The text focuses on improving patient experience, seamless care, and integration within the hospital system, with a secondary focus on breaking down barriers in healthcare.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Teaching Hospital,FALSE,1,University Health Network (UHN),947
947,University Health Network (UHN),Solutions Beyond Boundaries,"Solutions Beyond Boundaries. THE_HOSPITAL is leading the charge for radical innovation. That means investing in discovery like never before. New opportunities and solutions abound, and THE_HOSPITAL must nurture and convert those.. Accelerate Research and Innovation: Create bold, breakthrough science-driven solutions to the world, improving outcomes for patients and health care systems globally.. Set Global Health Standards: Share our research, knowledge and innovations globally to redefine best practices and elevate health outcomes everywhere.. Transform Health Education: Focus on team-based, collaborative education that prepares learners for a rapidly evolving and exciting landscape.","RESEARCH, EDUCATION & ACADEMICS",DIGITAL HEALTH & INNOVATION,"The text focuses on research, global sharing of knowledge, innovation and transforming health education, aligning with research, digital health (due to innovation) and academics.","Research, Education & Academics","Research, Education & Academics",Teaching Hospital,FALSE,1,University Health Network (UHN),947
947,University Health Network (UHN),Alignment For Impact,"Alignment For Impact. To create lasting change, we will align our resources, partnerships and technologies where they will have the greatest impact. THE_HOSPITAL is called to drive real, transformative solutions that leverage the privilege of caring for patients, educating the health care providers and students of tomorrow, pursuing discovery and adoption. The future is here – and THE_HOSPITAL is bringing it to life.. High-Impact Partnerships: Forge strategic alliances that will amplify our efforts and drive widespread, meaningful results.. Harness Technology to Revolutionize Care: Integrate AI and digital tools to enhance the precision, speed and personalization of treatment, from diagnosis to recovery.. Build a Thriving Health Care Ecosystem: Foster an interconnected system that accelerates progress and ensures sustainable improvements in health worldwide and addresses the translation, adoption and commercialization of scientific discoveries for people in Canada and around the world.",INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,DIGITAL HEALTH & INNOVATION,"The text focuses on strategic alliances and building an interconnected health system, alongside the integration of AI and digital tools for enhanced care.",Integration & Partnerships,Integration & Partnerships,Teaching Hospital,FALSE,1,University Health Network (UHN),947
957,Quinte Health,Care,"Care. The best care possible, created with patients and their caregivers, our teams, and communities.. - Use innovation, imagination and technology to enable the best possible care and make work easier: - Have a ‘nothing about us without us’ culture, where people are engaged in decisions that impact them: - Ensure everyone connected to the hospital is united in our pursuit of excellent care.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,DIGITAL HEALTH & INNOVATION,"This text focuses on providing the best possible care, using innovation and technology to improve care delivery, and engaging people in decisions related to care, highlighting both patient care excellence and the use of digital tools.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Quinte Health,957
957,Quinte Health,Compassion,"Compassion. Humanity and kindness guide the way we lead, care, partner and support one another.. - Care for each other and leave no one alone: - Have everyone coming to the hospital feeling welcomed, safe and empowered: - See the whole person and ensure equity and inclusion, while celebrating diversity.",ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,HEALTH EQUITY & SOCIAL ACCOUNTABILITY,"This focuses on the organization's values of compassion, inclusion, and equity.",Org Culture & Governance,Org Culture & Governance,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Quinte Health,957
957,Quinte Health,Connection,"Connection. Community hospitals building health and wellness together through partnerships and connections.. - Together with our full range of community partners, build stronger, sustainable communities: - As one the hospital team, and with our partners, deliver high-quality care and exceptional experiences: - Work across the health system to provide equitable access to care, as close to home as possible.",INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,POPULATION & COMMUNITY HEALTH,"The focus on partnerships and community hospitals building health and wellness together, along with delivering care close to home, aligns with integration and community health.",Integration & Partnerships,Integration & Partnerships,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Quinte Health,957
957,Quinte Health,Our People,"Our People. A relentless commitment to our people and teams to support them to grow, thrive and lead.. - Celebrate achievements – large and small – and recognize the efforts of our teams: - Empower teams to improve the work, care and experience for all: - Ensure a stable and future-focused the hospital team, in a culture that prioritizes safety and life-friendly work: - Support our people to be creative, learn and lead.",WORKFORCE SUSTAINABILITY,ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,"The text focuses on supporting, empowering, and recognizing the hospital's workforce, fostering a positive and future-focused culture.",Workforce Sustainability,Workforce Sustainability,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,Quinte Health,957
632,NORTH YORK GENERAL,People And Culture,"People And Culture. Being a place where the best people want to learn, grow and innovate.. Be a destination of choice attracting top talent to our team.: Be a destination of choice for people to grow their careers.",WORKFORCE SUSTAINABILITY,ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,"This text focuses on attracting talent, promoting growth, and being a desirable workplace, aligning with workforce sustainability and organizational culture.",Workforce Sustainability,Workforce Sustainability,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,NORTH YORK GENERAL,632
632,NORTH YORK GENERAL,Specialized Excellence,"Specialized Excellence. Innovating across clinical pathways, grounded in quality for global impact.. Ensure timely access for high-needs populations through partnerships and integration.: Advance frontline practice through digital innovation and expanding our research focused on addressing specific local community health needs.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,"The text focuses on clinical pathway innovation and quality, access for high-needs populations via partnerships, and research focused on community health.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,NORTH YORK GENERAL,632
632,NORTH YORK GENERAL,Health Equity,"Health Equity. Understanding and achieving health equity in access, treatment and outcomes.. Identify and address inequities through high-quality data, evidence and deep engagement of cultural and underserved communities.: Connect underserved communities to care.",HEALTH EQUITY & SOCIAL ACCOUNTABILITY,ACCESS & CAPACITY,"The text explicitly mentions ""health equity"" and addressing inequities in access, treatment, and outcomes, while also focusing on connecting underserved communities to care.",Health Equity & Social Accountability,Health Equity & Social Accountability,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,NORTH YORK GENERAL,632
632,NORTH YORK GENERAL,Connected Care,"Connected Care. Delivering an integrated, continuous healthcare journey that supports each person across primary, home, community, and hospital care.. Empower patients and professionals by expanding hospital services and using simple yet powerful AI and digital tools to connect people with care.: Deliver convenient, seamless and comprehensive care through partnerships.",INTEGRATION & PARTNERSHIPS,DIGITAL HEALTH & INNOVATION,The text focuses on integrating care across different settings through partnerships and leveraging AI and digital tools.,Integration & Partnerships,Integration & Partnerships,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,NORTH YORK GENERAL,632
632,NORTH YORK GENERAL,Personalized Experiences,"Personalized Experiences. Delivering personalized and compassionate care for our patients, residents and families.. Engage patients, providers and partners to better understand individual needs.: Co-design spaces and systems with the people they are meant for and empower teams to provide unparalleled experiences.",PATIENT CARE EXCELLENCE,ORG CULTURE & GOVERNANCE,"The focus is on delivering personalized and compassionate care, aligning with patient experience and the co-design aspect relates to organizational culture.",Patient Care Excellence,Patient Care Excellence,Large Community Hospital,FALSE,1,NORTH YORK GENERAL,632
